room_title: Escape room "The King’s Keep" by Next-Gen Escape in Fresno
room_description:
Accused of a crime you didn’t commit, you have one hour before the executioner returns to administer the King’s justice. Get out and prove your innocence!
A one of a kind experience in a fantastic set! For fans of Game of Thrones, Harry Potter, The Elder Scrolls, and Dungeons and Dragons.
